{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Every year in the United States alone,"},{"time":3470,"text":"2,077,000 couples make\na legal and spiritual decision"},{"time":9986,"text":"to spend the rest\nof their lives together --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13882,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":15056,"text":"And not to have sex with anyone else."},{"time":19500,"text":"Ever."},{"time":21140,"text":"He buys a ring, she buys a dress."},{"time":24799,"text":"They go shopping for all sorts of things."},{"time":28240,"text":"She takes him to Arthur Murray\nfor ballroom-dancing lessons."},{"time":33688,"text":"And the big day comes."},{"time":35244,"text":"And they'll stand before God and family"},{"time":38168,"text":"and some guy her dad\nonce did business with,"},{"time":41132,"text":"and they'll vow that nothing --"},{"time":43741,"text":"not abject poverty,"},{"time":46045,"text":"not life-threatening illness,"},{"time":48193,"text":"not complete and utter misery --"},{"time":51629,"text":"will ever put the tiniest damper\non their eternal love and devotion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56983,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":58755,"text":"These optimistic young bastards\npromise to honor and cherish each other"},{"time":63065,"text":"through hot flashes and midlife crises"},{"time":66892,"text":"and a cumulative 50-pound weight gain,"},{"time":70356,"text":"until that far-off day, when one of them\nis finally able to rest in peace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77415,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":78589,"text":"You know, because they can't hear\nthe snoring anymore."},{"time":81527,"text":"And then they'll get stupid drunk"},{"time":83355,"text":"and smash cake in each other's faces\nand do the Macarena."},{"time":86483,"text":"And we'll be there,"},{"time":88110,"text":"showering them with towels and toasters\nand drinking their free booze"},{"time":92544,"text":"and throwing birdseed at them\nevery single time ..."},{"time":96718,"text":"even though we know, statistically,"},{"time":100428,"text":"half of them will be divorced\nwithin a decade."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103547,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106126,"text":"Of course, the other half won't, right?"},{"time":108833,"text":"They'll keep forgetting anniversaries"},{"time":111832,"text":"and arguing about where to spend holidays"},{"time":114344,"text":"and debating --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":115531,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":116623,"text":"Which way the toilet paper\nshould come off of the roll."},{"time":120787,"text":"And some of them will even still\nbe enjoying each other's company"},{"time":126301,"text":"when neither of them can chew\nsolid food anymore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129749,"text":"And researchers want to know why."},{"time":132669,"text":"I mean, look -- it doesn't take\na double-blind, placebo-controlled study"},{"time":136201,"text":"to figure out what makes\na marriage not work:"},{"time":139160,"text":"disrespect, boredom,"},{"time":142403,"text":"too much time on Facebook,"},{"time":144153,"text":"having sex with other people."},{"time":146193,"text":"But you can have the exact\nopposite of all of those things --"},{"time":149727,"text":"respect, excitement,"},{"time":152495,"text":"a broken Internet connection,"},{"time":154690,"text":"mind-numbing monogamy --"},{"time":158550,"text":"and the thing still can go\nto hell in a handbasket."},{"time":161723,"text":"So, what's going on when it doesn't?"},{"time":165210,"text":"What do the folks who make it all the way\nto side-by-side burial plots"},{"time":169254,"text":"have in common?"},{"time":170841,"text":"What are they doing right?"},{"time":172575,"text":"What can we learn from them?"},{"time":175499,"text":"And if you're still happily sleeping solo,"},{"time":179282,"text":"why should you stop what you're doing\nand make it your life's work"},{"time":183718,"text":"to find that one special person"},{"time":186435,"text":"that you can annoy\nfor the rest of your life?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":189569,"text":"Well, researchers spend\nbillions of your tax dollars"},{"time":192813,"text":"trying to figure that out."},{"time":194673,"text":"They stalk blissful couples"},{"time":196664,"text":"and study their every move and mannerism."},{"time":199890,"text":"And they try to pinpoint\nwhat it is that sets them apart"},{"time":203702,"text":"from their miserable\nneighbors and friends."},{"time":205969,"text":"And it turns out, the success stories\nshare a few similarities,"},{"time":211802,"text":"beyond that they don't have sex\nwith other people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214928,"text":"For instance, in the happiest marriages,"},{"time":217977,"text":"the wife is thinner and better-looking"},{"time":219839,"text":"than the husband."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221029,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":222143,"text":"Obvious. Right?"},{"time":224384,"text":"It's obvious that this leads\nto marital bliss,"},{"time":226920,"text":"because women -- we care a great deal\nabout being thin and good-looking,"},{"time":230597,"text":"whereas men mostly care about sex,"},{"time":234122,"text":"ideally, with women who are thinner\nand better looking than they are."},{"time":238241,"text":"The beauty of this research, though,"},{"time":240012,"text":"is that no one is suggesting\nthat women have to be thin to be happy."},{"time":244289,"text":"We just have to be thinner\nthan our partners."},{"time":246723,"text":"So instead of all that laborious\ndieting and exercising,"},{"time":251247,"text":"we just need to wait\nfor them to get fat --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":253478,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":254774,"text":"Maybe bake a few pies."},{"time":256672,"text":"This is good information to have,\nand it's not that complicated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":260049,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":261099,"text":"Research also suggests"},{"time":263235,"text":"that the happiest couples are the ones\nthat focus on the positives."},{"time":268450,"text":"For example: the happy wife."},{"time":270038,"text":"Instead of pointing out\nher husband's growing gut"},{"time":272404,"text":"or suggesting he go for a run,"},{"time":274989,"text":"she might say,"},{"time":276358,"text":"\"Wow, honey, thank you\nfor going out of your way"},{"time":279666,"text":"to make me relatively thinner.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":281557,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":282585,"text":"These are couples\nwho can find good in any situation."},{"time":285794,"text":"\"Yeah, it was devastating\nwhen we lost everything in that fire."},{"time":291046,"text":"But it's kind of nice sleeping\nout here under the stars."},{"time":293869,"text":"And it's a good thing you've got\nall that body fat to keep us warm.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":297095,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":298322,"text":"One of my favorite studies found"},{"time":300244,"text":"that the more willing\na husband is to do housework,"},{"time":303395,"text":"the more attractive\nhis wife will find him."},{"time":307162,"text":"Because we needed a study to tell us this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309423,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":310719,"text":"But here's what's going on here."},{"time":312279,"text":"The more attractive she finds him,\nthe more sex they have;"},{"time":315443,"text":"the more sex they have,\nthe nicer he is to her;"},{"time":317889,"text":"the nicer he is to her,"},{"time":319613,"text":"the less she nags him\nabout leaving wet towels on the bed,"},{"time":322447,"text":"and ultimately,\nthey live happily ever after."},{"time":325549,"text":"In other words, men,\nyou might want to pick it up a notch"},{"time":328959,"text":"in the domestic department."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331600,"text":"Here's an interesting one."},{"time":333365,"text":"One study found that people\nwho smile in childhood photographs"},{"time":338446,"text":"are less likely to get a divorce."},{"time":341584,"text":"This is an actual study,\nand let me clarify:"},{"time":344449,"text":"the researchers were not looking\nat documented self-reports"},{"time":347754,"text":"of childhood happiness,"},{"time":349058,"text":"or even studying old journals."},{"time":351110,"text":"The data were based entirely\non whether people looked happy"},{"time":355705,"text":"in these early pictures."},{"time":357786,"text":"Now, I don't know how old all of you are,\nbut when I was a kid,"},{"time":362311,"text":"your parents took pictures\nwith a special kind of camera"},{"time":365049,"text":"that held something called \"film.\""},{"time":367800,"text":"And, by God, film was expensive."},{"time":371504,"text":"They didn't take 300 shots of you\nin that rapid-fire digital video mode"},{"time":376308,"text":"and then pick out the nicest,\nsmiliest one for the Christmas card."},{"time":380927,"text":"Oh, no."},{"time":383134,"text":"They dressed you up, they lined you up,"},{"time":385033,"text":"and you smiled for the fucking camera\nlike they told you to"},{"time":387854,"text":"or you could kiss\nyour birthday party goodbye."},{"time":390063,"text":"But still, I have a huge pile\nof fake happy childhood pictures"},{"time":393631,"text":"and I'm glad they make me less likely\nthan some people to get a divorce."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398355,"text":"So, what else can you do\nto safeguard your marriage?"},{"time":402523,"text":"Do not win an Oscar for best actress."}]},{"cues":[{"time":405794,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":407635,"text":"I'm serious."},{"time":408853,"text":"Bettie Davis, Joan Crawford,\nHalle Berry, Hilary Swank,"},{"time":411919,"text":"Sandra Bullock, Reese Witherspoon --"},{"time":414129,"text":"all of them single,\nsoon after taking home that statue."},{"time":417685,"text":"They actually call it the Oscar curse."},{"time":420075,"text":"It is the marriage kiss of death\nand something that should be avoided."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424718,"text":"And it's not just successfully\nstarring in films that's dangerous."},{"time":428764,"text":"It turns out, merely watching\na romantic comedy"},{"time":432695,"text":"causes relationship\nsatisfaction to plummet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435838,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":437312,"text":"Apparently, the bitter realization\nthat maybe it could happen to us,"},{"time":443205,"text":"but it obviously hasn't\nand it probably never will,"},{"time":445841,"text":"makes our lives seem\nunbearably grim in comparison."},{"time":449817,"text":"And theoretically,"},{"time":451262,"text":"I suppose if we opt for a film\nwhere someone gets brutally murdered"},{"time":454551,"text":"or dies in a fiery car crash,"},{"time":456973,"text":"we are more likely to walk out\nof that theater"},{"time":459141,"text":"feeling like we've got it pretty good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461103,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":463172,"text":"Drinking alcohol, it seems,\nis bad for your marriage."},{"time":468442,"text":"Yeah."},{"time":470356,"text":"I can't tell you anymore about that one"},{"time":472248,"text":"because I stopped reading it\nat the headline."},{"time":474387,"text":"But here's a scary one:\ndivorce is contagious."},{"time":478671,"text":"That's right, when you have\na close couple friend split up,"},{"time":481509,"text":"it increases your chances\nof getting a divorce by 75 percent."},{"time":487023,"text":"Now, I have to say,\nI don't get this one at all."},{"time":490213,"text":"My husband and I have watched\nquite a few friends divide their assets"},{"time":494897,"text":"and then struggle\nwith being our age and single"},{"time":499535,"text":"in an age of sexting\nand Viagra and eHarmony."},{"time":504362,"text":"And I'm thinking they've done\nmore for my marriage"},{"time":506784,"text":"than a lifetime of therapy ever could."}]},{"cues":[{"time":509794,"text":"So now you may be wondering:\nWhy does anyone get married ever?"},{"time":515478,"text":"Well, the US federal government\ncounts more than a thousand legal benefits"},{"time":520653,"text":"to being someone's spouse."},{"time":522505,"text":"A list that includes\nvisitation rights in jail,"},{"time":525207,"text":"but hopefully, you'll never need that one."},{"time":527612,"text":"But beyond the profound federal perks,"},{"time":531860,"text":"married people make more money."},{"time":534267,"text":"We're healthier,\nphysically and emotionally."},{"time":538398,"text":"We produce happier, more stable\nand more successful kids."},{"time":543906,"text":"We have more sex than our supposedly\nswinging single friends,"},{"time":548045,"text":"believe it or not."},{"time":549783,"text":"We even live longer,"},{"time":551000,"text":"which is a pretty compelling argument\nfor marrying someone you like a lot"},{"time":556179,"text":"in the first place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557427,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":558460,"text":"Now, if you're not currently experiencing\nthe joy of the joint tax return,"},{"time":564464,"text":"I can't tell you how to find\na chore-loving person"},{"time":567982,"text":"of the approximately ideal size\nand attractiveness,"},{"time":570409,"text":"who prefers horror movies"},{"time":571711,"text":"and doesn't have a lot of friends\nhovering on the brink of divorce,"},{"time":574900,"text":"but I can only encourage you to try,"},{"time":577000,"text":"because the benefits, as I've pointed out,"},{"time":579868,"text":"are significant."},{"time":581928,"text":"The bottom line is: whether you're in it\nor you're searching for it,"},{"time":585198,"text":"I believe marriage is an institution\nworth pursuing and protecting."},{"time":590448,"text":"So I hope you'll use the information\nI've given you today"},{"time":593157,"text":"to weigh your personal strengths\nagainst your own risk factors."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596695,"text":"For instance, in my marriage,\nI'd say I'm doing OK."},{"time":601329,"text":"One the one hand,"},{"time":602750,"text":"I have a husband who's annoyingly lean\nand incredibly handsome."},{"time":607217,"text":"So I'm obviously going\nto need fatten him up."},{"time":610122,"text":"And like I said, we have\nthose divorced friends"},{"time":612873,"text":"who may secretly or subconsciously\nbe trying to break us up."},{"time":616726,"text":"So we have to keep an eye on that."},{"time":620201,"text":"And we do like a cocktail or two."},{"time":622848,"text":"On the other hand,"},{"time":624261,"text":"I have the fake happy picture thing."},{"time":626528,"text":"And also, my husband does\na lot around the house,"},{"time":630167,"text":"and would happily never see\nanother romantic comedy"},{"time":633786,"text":"as long as he lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":635056,"text":"So I've got all those things going for me."},{"time":637658,"text":"But just in case,"},{"time":638902,"text":"I plan to work extra hard\nto not win an Oscar anytime soon."},{"time":644636,"text":"And for the good of your relationships,"},{"time":646728,"text":"I would encourage you to do the same."},{"time":649611,"text":"I'll see you at the bar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":650901,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":652096,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}